version_description: This is a version whithout capo.
I only have some doubt on guitar solo part chords, but they seem to work anyway.
My version is correct... the rest (as it relates to chords are incorrect...
You can play along with the song from CD. There is no capo used and if you can sing like Steve Lukather this version is perfect.
There were no tabs of this amazing song at ultimate guitar, so I wanted to change that.
